Uncanny Dodge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES												DESC:You can react to danger before your senses would normally allow you to do so. You retain your Dexterity bonus to AC (If any) even if you are caught flat-footed or struck by an invisible attacker. You still lose your AC bonus if immobilized.																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.40
Improved Uncanny Dodge	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES												DESC:You can no longer be flanked. This defense denies another rogue the ability to sneak attack you, unless the attacker is a rogue of at least level %1.|UncannyDodgeFlankingLevel																																							BONUS:VAR|UncannyDodgeFlankingLevel|4|TYPE=OnceOnly	SOURCEPAGE:p.40


